      <div class="bg-white border border-teal-light px-6 py-10 md:px-10 md:py-12">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
          <h2 class="font-body text-3xl font-bold text-charcoal">Natural-Looking Results Matter</h2>
          <p class="text-charcoal/70 leading-8">Patients often tell us they want their smile to look better without looking fake. That is why we pay attention to tooth shape, gum display, bite, facial balance, and the small details that make dentistry blend in. Cosmetic dentistry should give you confidence, not make you feel like you are wearing someone else's smile.</p>
