            <h2 class="font-body text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal md:min-h-[4rem]">What Happens at a Cosmetic Consultation?</h2>
            <p class="text-charcoal/70 leading-8 mt-4">We start by listening to what bothers you and what you hope to change. From there, we evaluate your teeth, gums, bite, existing dental work, and smile photos. If there are health concerns, we explain what should be handled first. If several cosmetic paths are possible, we compare them clearly so the plan matches your expectations and budget.</p>
