          <div class="flex flex-col">
            <h2 class="font-body text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal md:min-h-[4rem]">Is Cosmetic Dentistry Right for You?</h2>
            <p class="text-charcoal/70 leading-8 mt-4">Cosmetic dentistry can be a good fit if you avoid smiling, hide your teeth in photos, feel self-conscious about old dental work, or want a more polished look for personal or professional reasons. The right plan may be small and conservative, or it may involve a larger transformation. Either way, the first step is a conversation.</p>
